{"tid":1536071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"帶個概念俾前線 狗屋監控中心","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:56:52.000Z","uid":264281,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1969ac60d42719de46879cc1b61b5d8bfea49da9","tid":1536071,"uid":264281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"大概係咁既環境（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DrzdHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DrzdHC.jpg&h=c957b03b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VjZ5knG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjZ5knG.jpg&h=af54b3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢到係7*24小時運作 <br />\n而且會mon實所有新聞直播<br />\n包括某啲有名既Facebook group, YouTube, IG直播<br />\n會有直線通訊系統同前線指揮部做實時通訊<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n記者直播=狗望到<br />\n記者收音=狗聽到<br />\n<br />\n重申絕對尊重前線決定<br />\n只希望前線做決定時要留意鏡頭！<br />\n甚至利用記者 聲東擊西"},{"pid":"1e871275149d2a67919162a2bd3fa029b99c67e0","tid":1536071,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br